THAT the Oklahoma State Senate hereby recognizes and honors the
essential role teachers play in building a stronger future for
Oklahoma and the nation, and designates the week of May 5 through
May 9, 2025, as Teacher Appreciation Week in the State of Oklahoma.
Adopted by the Senate the 8th day of May, 2025.
